* &quot;The Golden Touch&quot;, a Walt Disney &quot;Silly Symphony&quot; cartoon based on the Greek myth of King Midas
* &quot;The Chocolate Touch&quot;, a children&#x27;s book about a boy who turns everything he touches to chocolate

